title: No Retreat, No Surrender: The Fan Cut
description:
Do you love 'No Retreat, No Surrender' but hated the DVD version? Yeah, me too. It
was one of my favourite movies when I was a kid. When it was released on DVD back
in 2004 I was very disappointed with what I saw. Although the picture was slightly
improved, there were so many differences that it felt like a completely different
movie. So I decided to make my own cut to resurrect the original version.
